Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格纳...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是拉格纳耶~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见 呃 之前...
